insert into public.email_templates (key, name, flow_key, subject, body_text, body_html, variables, updated_at) values (
  $K$doctor_bmh_anatomic_pathologist$K$,
  $N$Doctor · Best matched · Anatomic Pathologist$N$,
  'profile_sent',
  $S$Best matched Hospitals for Anatomic Pathologist in the UAE - Allocation Assist$S$,
  $BT$Hi Dr. {{doctor_name}},

I hope you are doing well.

From our experience in the market, below are the hospitals that we feel are most relevant and suitable for your speciality and training. We have recommended your profile to these hospitals. Please see the information guide provided for each hospital to find out more about their facilities.

For a Anatomic Pathologist, the most appropriate hospitals are those with specialized Anatomic Pathology departments such as:
In Dubai:
American Hospital - Known for its advanced diagnostic and pathology services, including surgical pathology.
Clemenceau Hospital - High-standard pathology services as part of its diagnostic departments.
Rashid Hospital - Major government hospital with comprehensive anatomic pathology services, serving as a referral center for complex cases.
King's College Hospital - A highly relevant and reputable for pathologists, especially those interested in working within a prestigious, internationally affiliated healthcare setting.
NMC Hospitals (Dubai & Abu Dhabi) - They are recognized for their high standards of care, modern infrastructure, and a wide range of specialties, including pathology.
Mediclinic Hospitals (Dubai & Abu Dhabi) - Private hospital with well-established anatomic pathology labs.
In Abu Dhabi:
Sheikh Shakhbout Medical City - One of the largest government hospitals with extensive anatomic pathology facilities.
Sheikh Khalifa Medical City - Highly relevant and one of the top institutions in the UAE for pathologists.
Sheikh Tahnoon Medical City - It aims to provide comprehensive healthcare services, including specialized fields, and is designed to serve as a major medical hub in the region.
Mubadala Group - Known for high-quality diagnostic services and pathology.
Burjeel Medical Group (Burjeel Medical City, Burjeel Abu Dhabi & Burjeel Al Ain) - Private hospital with advanced diagnostic labs, including surgical pathology.
In Sharjah and Fujairah:
Sharjah University Hospital - A key provider of pathology services in Sharjah.
Al Sharq Hospital (Fujairah) - Offers diagnostic and pathology services.

However the UAE is a very progressive country with a rapidly evolving healthcare sector and sometimes the hospitals have unannounced plans to build departments, so we also recommend introducing our Doctors' profiles to other leading hospitals in case they have plans in the future.

Here is an entire list of our hospital network in the UAE:

In Dubai:
Dubai Health Authority - https://dubaihealth.ae/hospitals
American Hospital - https://www.ahdubai.com/about
