  $S$Best matched Hospitals for Critical Care Medicine in the UAE - Allocation Assist$S$,
  $BT$Hi Dr. {{doctor_name}},

I hope you are doing well.

From our experience in the market, below are the hospitals that we feel are most relevant and suitable for your speciality and training. We have recommended your profile to these hospitals. Please see the information guide provided for each hospital to find out more about their facilities.

For a Critical Care, the most appropriate hospitals are those with specialized Critical Care departments such as:
In Dubai:
American Hospital - Renowned for high-quality medical care, advanced ICU facilities, and international standards.
King's College Hospital - A well-regarded medical center affiliated with London's renowned hospital, offering comprehensive critical care services.
Rashid Hospital - Major government hospital with extensive emergency and critical care services.
Clemenceau Hospital - Part of Johns Hopkins Medicine International, with high standards in critical care.
Mediclinic Hospitals (Dubai & Abu Dhabi) - Well-established private hospital with advanced critical care services.
NMC Hospitals (Dubai & Abu Dhabi) - Well-known healthcare providers in the UAE, offering a wide range of medical services, including critical care.
In Abu Dhabi:
Sheikh Shakhbout Medical City – A leading government hospital with advanced critical care and specialized services.
Sheikh Khalifa Medical City - Major tertiary hospital with extensive ICU and critical care services.
Sheikh Tahnoon Medical City - A healthcare facility in the UAE that is designed to provide comprehensive medical services, including critical care.
Burjeel Medical Group (Burjeel Medical City, Burjeel Abu Dhabi & Burjeel Al Ain) - Known for high-quality private healthcare and critical care services.
Mubadala Group - Offers advanced healthcare services including critical care.
Tawam Hospital - Affiliated with Johns Hopkins Medicine, specializing in trauma, cardiac, and critical care.
In Sharjah and Fujairah:
Sharjah University Hospital - Reputable for comprehensive care services.
Al Sharq Hospital (Fujairah) - Known for general and critical care.

However the UAE is a very progressive country with a rapidly evolving healthcare sector and sometimes the hospitals have unannounced plans to build departments, so we also recommend introducing our Doctors' profiles to other leading hospitals in case they have plans in the future.

Here is an entire list of our hospital network in the UAE:

