  'profile_sent',
  $S$Best matched Hospitals for Breast Radiologist in the UAE - Allocation Assist$S$,
  $BT$Hi Dr. {{doctor_name}},

I hope you are doing well.

From our experience in the market, below are the hospitals that we feel are most relevant and suitable for your speciality and training. We have recommended your profile to these hospitals. Please see the information guide provided for each hospital to find out more about their facilities.

For a breast radiologist, the most appropriate hospitals are those with specialized breast radiology departments such as:
In Dubai:
American Hospital - Known for high-quality healthcare and advanced imaging technology.
King's College Hospital - A reputable healthcare institution known for its high standards of medical care and specialized services.
Al Zahra Hospital - Known as the only private hospital in the UAE with a JCI‑accredited dedicated Breast Cancer Center. Offers digital mammography, 3D mammography, breast MRI, ultrasound, biopsies, clip localization, and triple assessments through a multidisciplinary team.
Mediclinic Hospitals (Dubai & Abu Dhabi) - Part of a reputable healthcare group with advanced radiology facilities.
NMC Hospitals (Dubai & Abu Dhabi) - Well-equipped with modern radiology services.
Rashid Hospital - Offers comprehensive radiology services with specialized departments.
In Abu Dhabi:
Sheikh Shakhbout Medical City - Offers advanced diagnostic imaging services.
Sheikh Khalifa Medical City - Prominent in radiology and breast imaging.
Burjeel Medical Group (Burjeel Medical City, Burjeel Abu Dhabi & Burjeel Al Ain) - Known for comprehensive breast imaging services.
Tawam Hospital - part of SEHA's Breast Care Center. Recently renovated to offer state‑of‑the‑art breast imaging (digital mammography, ultrasound, MRI), image‑guided minimally invasive biopsies, reconstruction, genetic counseling, and comprehensive team-based care.
Mubadala Group - Modern facilities with advanced imaging services.
In Sharjah:
Sharjah University Hospital –In partnership with Gustave Roussy (France), this dedicated breast care center provides digital mammography, breast ultrasound, MRI, image‑guided interventional radiology, and multidisciplinary cancer care with genetic counseling and patient support programs.

However the UAE is a very progressive country with a rapidly evolving healthcare sector and sometimes the hospitals have unannounced plans to build departments, so we also recommend introducing our Doctors' profiles to other leading hospitals in case they have plans in the future.

