  $BT$Hi Dr. {{doctor_name}},

I hope you are doing well.

From our experience in the market, below are the hospitals that we feel are most relevant and suitable for your speciality and training. We have recommended your profile to these hospitals. Please see the information guide provided for each hospital to find out more about their facilities.

For a Cardiologist & Electrophysiologist, the most appropriate hospitals are those with specialized Cardiology & Electrophysiology departments such as:
In Dubai:
American Hospital - Known for its comprehensive cardiology department, including electrophysiology and advanced cardiac interventions.
Fakeeh University Hospital - Integrated digital systems and high patient satisfaction.
King's College Hospital - Extension of the prestigious UK institution, offering a top-tier Heart & Vascular Institute which covers interventional cardiology, electrophysiology, cardiac surgery and advanced diagnostics.
Rashid Hospital - A government hospital with a large cardiology department offering specialized cardiac services, including electrophysiology.
NMC Hospitals (Dubai & Abu Dhabi) - Well known healthcare providers in the UAE, offering a wide range of medical services, including cardiology.
