  'profile_sent',
  $S$Best matched Hospitals for Emergency Medicine in the UAE - Allocation Assist$S$,
  $BT$Hi Dr. {{doctor_name}},

I hope you are doing well.

From our experience in the market, below are the hospitals that we feel are most relevant and suitable for your speciality and training. We have recommended your profile to these hospitals. Please see the information guide provided for each hospital to find out more about their facilities.

For an emergency medicine, the most appropriate hospitals are those with specialized emergency medicine departments such as:
In Dubai:
American Hospital - Known for excellent emergency services, advanced facilities, and experienced emergency physicians.
King's College Hospital - It offers a wide range of medical services, including emergency care and is known for its high standards and specialized medical expertise.
Rashid Hospital - One of Dubai’s flagship government hospitals with a comprehensive emergency department that handles a large volume of emergency cases.
Saudi German Hospital - Offers emergency medical services.
NMC Hospitals (Dubai & Abu Dhabi) - They have modern facilities and experienced medical staff, and they offer emergency services as part of their comprehensive care.
Mediclinic Hospitals (Dubai & Abu Dhabi) - Offers 24/7 emergency services with a focus on urgent care and trauma.
In Abu Dhabi:
Sheikh Shakhbout Medical City - Major government hospital with a dedicated emergency department, handling complex trauma and urgent cases.
Sheikh Khalifa Medical City - Well-equipped emergency department with 24/7 services.
Burjeel Medical Group (Burjeel Medical City, Burjeel Abu Dhabi & Burjeel Al Ain) - Provides comprehensive emergency services, including trauma and urgent care.
Reem Hospital - A new healthcare facility designed to serve the community with a range of medical services, including emergency care. It aims to provide comprehensive and accessible healthcare with modern infrastructure.
Tawam Hospital - Recognized for emergency and trauma services.
In Sharjah and Fujairah:
Sharjah University Hospital - Known for a reliable emergency department and urgent care services.
Al Sharq Hospital (Fujairah) - Provides emergency services suitable for urgent medical needs in the region.

However the UAE is a very progressive country with a rapidly evolving healthcare sector and sometimes the hospitals have unannounced plans to build departments, so we also recommend introducing our Doctors' profiles to other leading hospitals in case they have plans in the future.

Here is an entire list of our hospital network in the UAE:

In Dubai:
