From our experience in the market, below are the hospitals that we feel are most relevant and suitable for your speciality and training. We have recommended your profile to these hospitals. Please see the information guide provided for each hospital to find out more about their facilities.

For a Cardiologist, the most appropriate hospitals are those with specialized Cardiology departments such as:
In Dubai:
American Hospital - Known for advanced medical services, including cardiology.
Al Zahra Hospital - Among the top 10 hospitals in Dubai, JCI-accredited, with strong cardiology and neurology departments and solid patient satisfaction ratings.
Fakeeh University Hospital - Integrated digital systems and high patient satisfaction.
King's College Hospital - Extension of the prestigious UK institution, offering a top-tier Heart & Vascular Institute which covers interventional cardiology, electrophysiology, cardiac surgery and advanced diagnostics.
