Burjeel Medical Group (Burjeel Medical City, Burjeel Abu Dhabi & Burjeel Al Ain) - Known for cardiology and cardiac surgery
In Sharjah and Fujairah:
Sharjah University Hospital - Known for providing a range of medical services, including cardiology.
