  'profile_sent',
  $S$Best matched Hospitals for Gastroenterologist in the UAE - Allocation Assist$S$,
  $BT$Hi Dr. {{doctor_name}},

I hope you are doing well.

From our experience in the market, below are the hospitals that we feel are most relevant and suitable for your speciality and training. We have recommended your profile to these hospitals. Please see the information guide provided for each hospital to find out more about their facilities.

For a Gastroenterologist, the most appropriate hospitals are those with specialized Gastroenterology departments such as:
In Dubai:
American Hospital - Known for high-quality healthcare and specialized gastroenterology services.
Fakeeh University Hospital - Recognized for its comprehensive medical services, including gastroenterology.
King's College Hospital - Part of the larger King's College Hospital NHS Foundation Trust in London, which has a strong reputation for gastroenterology and gastrointestinal surgery.
NMC Hospitals (Dubai & Abu Dhabi) - They offer comprehensive gastroenterology services, including diagnostics, endoscopy, colonoscopy, and treatment of various gastrointestinal conditions.
Rashid Hospital - A major government hospital offering comprehensive gastroenterology services.
Mediclinic Hospitals (Dubai & Abu Dhabi) - Offers advanced gastroenterology diagnostics and treatments.
In Abu Dhabi:
Sheikh Shakhbout Medical City - A leading tertiary care hospital with comprehensive specialties, including gastroenterology and advanced endoscopy services.
Sheikh Khalifa Medical City - One of Abu Dhabi’s largest and most established hospitals, offering specialized gastroenterology services, advanced diagnostics and treatments.
Sheikh Tahnoon Medical City - It provides comprehensive healthcare services, including specialized departments that cater to gastroenterology.
Burjeel Medical Group (Burjeel Medical City, Burjeel Abu Dhabi & Burjeel Al Ain) - Private hospitals with experienced gastroenterologists and advanced outpatient services.
Tawam Hospital - Located near Abu Dhabi (Al Ain), Tawam is a renowned tertiary hospital with comprehensive gastroenterology and pediatric services.
In Sharjah and Fujairah:Sharjah University Hospital - A well-established medical facility affiliated with the University of Sharjah. It offers a range of medical services, including specialist departments such as internal medicine and gastroenterology.
Al Sharq Hospital (Fujairah) - Provides general and specialized gastroenterology services.

However the UAE is a very progressive country with a rapidly evolving healthcare sector and sometimes the hospitals have unannounced plans to build departments, so we also recommend introducing our Doctors' profiles to other leading hospitals in case they have plans in the future.

