  'profile_sent',
  $S$Best matched Hospitals for Fetal Medicine in the UAE - Allocation Assist$S$,
  $BT$Hi Dr. {{doctor_name}},

I hope you are doing well.

From our experience in the market, below are the hospitals that we feel are most relevant and suitable for your speciality and training. We have recommended your profile to these hospitals. Please see the information guide provided for each hospital to find out more about their facilities.

For a Fetal Medicine, the most appropriate hospitals are those with specialized Fetal Medicine departments such as:
In Dubai:
American Hospital - Known for comprehensive maternal-fetal medicine services, advanced diagnostics, and a team of specialists.
Al Zahra Hospital - Full-service OB-GYN department with advanced neonatal ICU, birthing suites and fetal medicine.
Fakeeh University Hospital - It provides quality obstetric care and prenatal services, including ultrasounds and high-risk pregnancy management.
King's College Hospital - It provides comprehensive maternal and fetal care, including prenatal diagnostics, high-risk pregnancy management and fetal ultrasound scans.
Mediclinic Hospitals (Dubai & Abu Dhabi) - Offers specialized obstetrics and fetal medicine services.
Rashid Hospital - A major government hospital with specialized maternal and fetal care units.
NMC Hospitals (Dubai & Abu Dhabi) - One of the well-known private hospitals offering comprehensive OB-GYN care.
In Abu Dhabi:
Sheikh Shakhbout Medical City - A leading hospital with specialized maternal and fetal care.
Sheikh Khalifa Medical City - Offers comprehensive obstetric and fetal medicine services.
Sheikh Tahnoon Medical City - Known for providing high-quality healthcare services, including maternal and fetal care.
Reem Hospital - Provides standard prenatal and obstetric services, including ultrasounds and high-risk pregnancy management.
Burjeel Medical Group (Burjeel Medical City, Burjeel Abu Dhabi & Burjeel Al Ain) - Known for advanced maternal health services and fetal medicine.
In Sharjah:
Sharjah University Hospital - Has a good reputation for maternal health services.

However the UAE is a very progressive country with a rapidly evolving healthcare sector and sometimes the hospitals have unannounced plans to build departments, so we also recommend introducing our Doctors' profiles to other leading hospitals in case they have plans in the future.

Here is an entire list of our hospital network in the UAE:

