insert into public.email_templates (key, name, flow_key, subject, body_text, body_html, variables, updated_at) values (
  $K$doctor_bmh_obgyn$K$,
  $N$Doctor · Best matched · OBGYN$N$,
  'profile_sent',
  $S$Best matched Hospitals for OBGYN in the UAE - Allocation Assist$S$,
  $BT$Hi Dr. {{doctor_name}},

I hope you are doing well.

From our experience in the market, below are the hospitals that we feel are most relevant and suitable for your speciality and training. We have recommended your profile to these hospitals. Please see the information guide provided for each hospital to find out more about their facilities.

For an OBGYN, the most appropriate hospitals are those with specialized OBGYN departments such as:
In Dubai:
American Hospital - Known for excellent medical standards and specialized OB-GYN services.
Al Zahra Hospital - Full-service OB-GYN department with advanced neonatal ICU, birthing suites, and fetal medicine.
Fakeeh University Hospital - Provides specialized OB-GYN services with advanced facilities.
King's College Hospital - Affiliated with King’s College London, renowned for women’s health and known for its UK-standard OB-GYN services.
Mediclinic Hospitals (Dubai & Abu Dhabi) - Offers comprehensive obstetrics and gynecology services.
Rashid Hospital - Government hospital with extensive OB-GYN and maternity services.
NMC Hospitals (Dubai & Abu Dhabi) - One of the well-known private hospitals offering comprehensive OB-GYN care.
In Abu Dhabi:
Sheikh Shakhbout Medical City - Major government hospital with specialized OB-GYN care.
Sheikh Khalifa Medical City - Known for comprehensive women's health services.
Burjeel Medical Group (Burjeel Medical City, Burjeel Abu Dhabi & Burjeel Al Ain) - Private hospital with advanced OB-GYN and maternity services.
In Sharjah and Fujairah:
Sharjah University Hospital - Teaching hospital with modern maternity wing and full OB-GYN services.
Al Sharq Hospital (Fujairah) - Offers comprehensive OB-GYN services, antenatal care, and modern delivery rooms.

However the UAE is a very progressive country with a rapidly evolving healthcare sector and sometimes the hospitals have unannounced plans to build departments, so we also recommend introducing our Doctors' profiles to other leading hospitals in case they have plans in the future.

Here is an entire list of our hospital network in the UAE:

In Dubai:
