  $S$Best matched Hospitals for Neurosurgeon in the UAE - Allocation Assist$S$,
  $BT$Hi Dr. {{doctor_name}},

I hope you are doing well.

From our experience in the market, below are the hospitals that we feel are most relevant and suitable for your speciality and training. We have recommended your profile to these hospitals. Please see the information guide provided for each hospital to find out more about their facilities.

For a Neurosurgeon, the most appropriate hospitals are those with Neurosurgery departments such as:
In Dubai:
American Hospital - Known for excellent specialized care and advanced medical technology, including neurosurgery.
Al Zahra Hospital - Offers neurology services and EEG/neurostimulation technologies; JCI accredited and recognized for quality care.
Fakeeh University Hospital - JCI‑accredited with top‑tier global ranking. Provides neurology and neurosurgery services among other specialties.
King's College Hospital - An extension of the renowned UK hospital, offering specialized neurosurgical services.
NMC Hospitals (Dubai & Abu Dhabi) - Well regarded private healthcare providers in the UAE, offering a range of specialized medical services, including neurosurgery.
Mediclinic Hospitals (Dubai & Abu Dhabi) - Offers a range of specialized neurosurgical procedures with experienced neurosurgeons.
In Abu Dhabi:
Sheikh Shakhbout Medical City - A large government hospital with comprehensive neurosurgical services.
Sheikh Khalifa Medical City - A highly reputable hospital with advanced medical facilities and a team of experienced specialists. It offers a wide range of specialized services, including neurosurgery.
Sheikh Tahnoon Medical City - Has a well established neurosurgical department with experienced specialists and modern facilities.
Burjeel Medical Group (Burjeel Medical City, Burjeel Abu Dhabi & Burjeel Al Ain) - Known for high quality healthcare and advanced neurosurgical treatments

However the UAE is a very progressive country with a rapidly evolving healthcare sector and sometimes the hospitals have unannounced plans to build departments, so we also recommend introducing our Doctors' profiles to other leading hospitals in case they have plans in the future.

Here is an entire list of our hospital network in the UAE:

