Mubadala Group - Offers specialized medical services, including ophthalmology.
In Sharjah and Fujairah:
Sharjah University Hospital - Provides ophthalmology services within its comprehensive healthcare offerings.
Al Sharq Hospital (Fujairah) - Offers ophthalmology among other specialties.

