Sheikh Khalifa Medical City - Major tertiary care hospital with nephrology departments.
Sheikh Tahnoon Medical City - A large, comprehensive healthcare facility that offers a wide range of medical services, including nephrology.
Mubadala Group - Known for high-quality nephrology care.
Burjeel Medical Group (Burjeel Medical City, Burjeel Abu Dhabi & Burjeel Al Ain) - Private hospital with advanced nephrology and dialysis services.
In Sharjah:
Sharjah University Hospital - Recognized for comprehensive healthcare including nephrology services.

However the UAE is a very progressive country with a rapidly evolving healthcare sector and sometimes the hospitals have unannounced plans to build departments, so we also recommend introducing our Doctors' profiles to other leading hospitals in case they have plans in the future.

