insert into public.email_templates (key, name, flow_key, subject, body_text, body_html, variables, updated_at) values (
  $K$doctor_bmh_pediatric_cardiologist$K$,
  $N$Doctor · Best matched · Pediatric Cardiologist$N$,
  'profile_sent',
  $S$Best matched Hospitals for Pediatric Cardiologist in the UAE - Allocation Assist$S$,
  $BT$Hi Dr. {{doctor_name}},

I hope you are doing well.

From our experience in the market, below are the hospitals that we feel are most relevant and suitable for your speciality and training. We have recommended your profile to these hospitals. Please see the information guide provided for each hospital to find out more about their facilities.

For a Pediatric Cardiologist, the most appropriate hospitals are those with specialized Pediatric Cardiology departments such as:
In Dubai:
American Hospital - Known for high-quality pediatric cardiology services, including interventional procedures.
Al Jalila Children's Hospital - A reputable and specialized pediatric hospital that offers a wide range of healthcare services for children, including pediatric cardiology.
King's College Hospital - Part of the UK-based King’s College Hospital, with a good reputation in cardiology.
Fakeeh University Hospital - Modern facilities and a focus on integrated healthcare services.
Clemenceau Hospital - A well-established healthcare facility offering a broad range of medical services, including pediatrics.
NMC Hospitals (Dubai & Abu Dhabi) - A reputable hospitals offering a wide range of medical services, including pediatrics.
Mediclinic Hospitals (Dubai & Abu Dhabi) - Both Mediclinic Dubai and Abu Dhabi are equipped with modern facilities, experienced pediatric cardiologists, and good reputations for general pediatric care.
In Abu Dhabi:
Sheikh Shakhbout Medical City - Offers comprehensive pediatric cardiology services, including interventional procedures.
Sheikh Khalifa Medical City - Known for advanced pediatric care, including cardiology and cardiothoracic surgery.
Burjeel Medical Group (Burjeel Medical City, Burjeel Abu Dhabi & Burjeel Al Ain) - Well-equipped with modern technology and experienced pediatric cardiologists. Suitable for many pediatric cardiac cases, including diagnostics and some interventions.
Mubadala Group - Mubadala’s network includes centers with pediatric cardiology services, and they are known for high-quality specialized care.
In Fujairah:
Al Sharq Hospital (Fujairah) - Growing reputation and modern facilities.
Sheikh Khalifa Hospital - A government hospital serving the Fujairah region, providing a range of medical services, including pediatrics.

However the UAE is a very progressive country with a rapidly evolving healthcare sector and sometimes the hospitals have unannounced plans to build departments, so we also recommend introducing our Doctors' profiles to other leading hospitals in case they have plans in the future.

Here is an entire list of our hospital network in the UAE:

