  'profile_sent',
  $S$Best matched Hospitals for Pediatric Oncologist in the UAE - Allocation Assist$S$,
  $BT$Hi Dr. {{doctor_name}},

I hope you are doing well.

From our experience in the market, below are the hospitals that we feel are most relevant and suitable for your speciality and training. We have recommended your profile to these hospitals. Please see the information guide provided for each hospital to find out more about their facilities.

For a Pediatric Oncologist, the most appropriate hospitals are those with specialized Pediatric Oncology departments such as:
In Dubai:
American Hospital - Known for its high-quality pediatric services and specialized departments, including pediatric oncology. The American Hospital has a good reputation internationally and offers comprehensive care.
Al Jalila Children's Hospital - A prominent healthcare facility dedicated to pediatric care, including specialized services for children with various medical conditions.
Mediclinic Hospitals (Dubai & Abu Dhabi) - It offers specialized pediatric care and has experienced pediatric oncologists.
King's College Hospital - A well-regarded healthcare facility known for its high-quality medical services, including pediatrics and various subspecialties.
Clemenceau Hospital - Primarily known for general and specialized medical services, it also offers pediatric care with experienced specialists.
NMC Hospitals (Dubai & Abu Dhabi) - A reputable healthcare facilities known for providing a wide range of medical services, including pediatrics.
In Abu Dhabi:
Sheikh Shakhbout Medical City - A leading hospital with comprehensive pediatric services, including oncology. It’s part of the SEHA network and has a team of specialized pediatric oncologists.
Sheikh Khalifa Medical City - Offers specialized pediatric services and has a good reputation for pediatric care.
Burjeel Medical Group (Burjeel Medical City, Burjeel Abu Dhabi & Burjeel Al Ain) - A reputable healthcare facilities within the Burjeel Group, known for providing comprehensive medical services.
Tawam Hospital - Known for its specialized services and affiliations with international institutions, offering pediatric oncology care.
In Sharjah and Fujairah:
Sharjah University Hospital - It provides pediatric services and is a reputable facility.
Al Sharq Hospital (Fujairah) - Provides general pediatric services.

However the UAE is a very progressive country with a rapidly evolving healthcare sector and sometimes the hospitals have unannounced plans to build departments, so we also recommend introducing our Doctors' profiles to other leading hospitals in case they have plans in the future.

