  $N$Doctor · Best matched · Pulmonologist & Critical Care Medicine$N$,
  'profile_sent',
  $S$Best matched Hospitals for Pulmonologist & Critical Care Medicine in the UAE - Allocation Assist$S$,
  $BT$Hi Dr. {{doctor_name}},

I hope you are doing well.

From our experience in the market, below are the hospitals that we feel are most relevant and suitable for your speciality and training. We have recommended your profile to these hospitals. Please see the information guide provided for each hospital to find out more about their facilities.

For a Pulmonologist & Critical Care Medicine, the most appropriate hospitals are those with specialized Pulmonology & Critical Care Medicine departments such as:
In Dubai:
American Hospital - Known for excellent specialized services, including pulmonology and critical care.
Al Zahra Hospital - A well-known healthcare facility, has experienced and specialized pulmonologists and intensivists on staff.
Fakeeh University Hospital - Holds a JCI accreditation and a five-star rating from Newsweek/Statista’s Global Hospital Rating—indicating exceptional quality in infrastructure and patient care.
King's College Hospital - High-quality medical care, strong international backing, and multidisciplinary expertise.
Rashid Hospital - A major public hospital with extensive critical care facilities.
NMC Hospitals (Dubai & Abu Dhabi) - Offers comprehensive healthcare services, including pulmonology and critical care. They have experienced specialists, modern facilities, andare accessible options for many patients.
