  $BT$Hi Dr. {{doctor_name}},

I hope you are doing well.

From our experience in the market, below are the hospitals that we feel are most relevant and suitable for your speciality and training. We have recommended your profile to these hospitals. Please see the information guide provided for each hospital to find out more about their facilities.

For a Urologist, the most appropriate hospitals are those with specialized Urology departments such as:
In Dubai:
American Hospital - Known for comprehensive specialties including urology, with advanced facilities and experienced specialists
Mediclinic Hospitals (Dubai & Abu Dhabi) - Known for providing a wide range of medical services, including urology.
Burjeel Hospital - Recognized for quality urology services backed by experienced consultants across locations
Rashid Hospital - A government hospital offering specialized urology services at a high standard.
Saudi German Hospital - High Yelp/Practo ratings and multiple experienced urologists.
NMC Hospitals (Dubai & Abu Dhabi) - Ranked among leading urology providers in Abu Dhabi, offering full range of services and recognized for strong diagnostic and surgical care
Clemenceau Hospital - Known for high-quality healthcare services, including urology.
In Abu Dhabi:
Sheikh Shakhbout Medical City - A leading government hospital with advanced urology services.
Sheikh Khalifa Medical City - A flagship SEHA hospital, JCI-accredited and supported by Cleveland Clinic management. Offers comprehensive urology services alongside its multidisciplinary team of specialists.
Burjeel Medical Group (Burjeel Medical City, Burjeel Abu Dhabi & Burjeel Al Ain) - Known for its large urology department with many senior consultants across locations, with advanced treatment capabilities
Tawam Hospital - Specialized in various fields including urology, affiliated with Johns Hopkins.

However the UAE is a very progressive country with a rapidly evolving healthcare sector and sometimes the hospitals have unannounced plans to build departments, so we also recommend introducing our Doctors' profiles to other leading hospitals in case they have plans in the future.

