  $S$Best matched Hospitals for PICU in the UAE - Allocation Assist$S$,
  $BT$Hi Dr. {{doctor_name}},

I hope you are doing well.

From our experience in the market, below are the hospitals that we feel are most relevant and suitable for your speciality and training. We have recommended your profile to these hospitals. Please see the information guide provided for each hospital to find out more about their facilities.

For a PICU, the most appropriate hospitals are those with specialized PICU departments such as:
In Dubai:
American Hospital - Known for high-quality healthcare and strong pediatric services.
Al Jalila Children's Hospital - Specializes exclusively in pediatric care, including PICU services.
Clemenceau Hospital - Known for excellent pediatric services and specialties.
Rashid Hospital - A major government hospital with a reputable pediatric and emergency department.
King's College Hospital - A reputable healthcare institution known for its high-quality medical services, including adult and pediatric care.
Saudi German Hospital - It offers specialized pediatric services, including intensive care units (PICU), staffed by experienced pediatric specialists and equipped with modern technology.
NMC Hospitals (Dubai & Abu Dhabi) - Well established healthcare providers known for offering a wide range of medical services, including pediatrics and intensive care.
Mediclinic Hospitals (Dubai & Abu Dhabi) - Offers extensive pediatric and ICU services.
In Abu Dhabi:
Sheikh Shakhbout Medical City - Large tertiary hospital with specialized pediatric ICU services.
Sheikh Khalifa Medical City - Known for comprehensive pediatric services including PICU.
Tawam Hospital - Renowned for pediatric care and critical care services.
Burjeel Medical Group (Burjeel Medical City, Burjeel Abu Dhabi & Burjeel Al Ain) - Known for providing high-quality medical services across the UAE. They are equipped with modern facilities and offer comprehensive pediatric care, including PICU services.
In Sharjah:
Sharjah University Hospital - Offers pediatric services, including intensive care.

However the UAE is a very progressive country with a rapidly evolving healthcare sector and sometimes the hospitals have unannounced plans to build departments, so we also recommend introducing our Doctors' profiles to other leading hospitals in case they have plans in the future.

Here is an entire list of our hospital network in the UAE:

