insert into public.email_templates (key, name, flow_key, subject, body_text, body_html, variables, updated_at) values (
  $K$doctor_bmh_plastic_surgeon$K$,
  $N$Doctor · Best matched · Plastic Surgeon$N$,
  'profile_sent',
  $S$Best matched Hospitals for Plastic Surgeon in the UAE - Allocation Assist$S$,
  $BT$Hi Dr. {{doctor_name}},

I hope you are doing well.

From our experience in the market, below are the hospitals that we feel are most relevant and suitable for your speciality and training. We have recommended your profile to these hospitals. Please see the information guide provided for each hospital to find out more about their facilities.

For a Plastic Surgeon, the most appropriate hospitals are those with specialized Plastic Surgery departments such as:
In Dubai:
American Hospital - Renowned for high-quality healthcare and experienced plastic surgeons.
Al Zahra Hospital - Offers cosmetic and reconstructive procedures, staffed by well‑regarded plastic surgeons.
Dubai London Clinic - Offers aesthetic and reconstructive procedures with experienced practitioners.
Fakeeh University Hospital - Home to a dedicated Department of Plastic, Hand & Reconstructive Surgery & Regenerative Medicine, offering both aesthetic and reconstructive procedures, including microsurgery and body contouring.
King's College Hospital - A well known medical institution with a reputation for high-quality healthcare services, including specialized surgical procedures.
NMC Hospital Dubai - Network includes CosmeSurge (specialized cosmetic surgery), meeting international standards and catering to medical‑tourist demand.
Saudi German Hospital - Provides liposuction, mommy makeovers, rhinoplasty and other aesthetic surgery services with experienced surgeons
Mediclinic Hospitals (Dubai & Abu Dhabi) - Known for specialized outpatient and surgical services, including plastic surgery.
In Abu Dhabi:
Sheikh Shakhbout Medical City - A leading hospital with a wide range of surgical specialties, including plastic surgery.
Sheikh Khalifa Medical City - A prominent and well-established medical facility in Abu Dhabi, known for its comprehensive healthcare services and advanced medical infrastructure.
Burjeel Medical Group (Burjeel Medical City, Burjeel Abu Dhabi & Burjeel Al Ain) - Reputable hospitals with advanced plastic surgery departments.
NMC Hospital Abu Dhabi - Included in rankings for cosmetic surgery in Abu Dhabi with personalized care and established teams of aesthetic/plastic surgeons.
In Sharjah:
